  "detailed_description": "Panda’s Village is a real-time strategy and survival game where you take on the role of a brave panda who must protect his village from the invasion of evil monkeys. You will need to build and upgrade houses, defenses, and stores, fight fierce monkeys, purchase and upgrade weapons and magic, and customize your panda with different outfits and accessories. Your goal is to save the village’s Capitol, the heart of your civilization, at all costs. If you die, you start over.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/98296de4bbb317b789b525e0434a1a15.webp?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/75203e027d6683362b698ebec7c80d22.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>Build and manage your village:</strong> Construct houses, shops, defenses, and more to provide resources and security for your panda population. Upgrade your buildings to increase their efficiency and durability. Balance your economy and military to ensure the survival of your village.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/6402fc06da69431b14294a271913b53b.poster.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/6402fc06da69431b14294a271913b53b.webm?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/6402fc06da69431b14294a271913b53b.mp4?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/ef0b998567de4ffe86f477c606f61af2.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>Fight and defend against the monkeys:</strong> The monkeys are relentless and will attack your village from all directions. Use your weapons and magic to fend them off, or recruit other pandas to join your army. Be careful, though, as the monkeys will also use their own tricks and tactics to try to destroy your Capitol.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/792bde2b68a0e5ba2deb04e11a7101eb.poster.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/792bde2b68a0e5ba2deb04e11a7101eb.webm?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/792bde2b68a0e5ba2deb04e11a7101eb.mp4?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/16e890e75b91d8c4d45f64049afd1f36.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>Purchase and upgrade your equipment:</strong> As you progress through the game, you will unlock new weapons and magic that will help you in your battles. You can buy them from the shop. You can also upgrade your panda's characteristics to be stronger, faster, and healthier.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/649bf924b275af4c1a6527e2e1e1819e.poster.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/649bf924b275af4c1a6527e2e1e1819e.webm?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/649bf924b275af4c1a6527e2e1e1819e.mp4?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/21a44d741a6b15c0077741480fc376fa.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>Customize your panda:</strong> Make your panda stand out from the crowd by choosing from a variety of outfits and accessories. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/7cdbde9d38cd38b15476c6be229af646.poster.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/7cdbde9d38cd38b15476c6be229af646.webm?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/7cdbde9d38cd38b15476c6be229af646.mp4?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/d110c0d7aba530ab220c2937fca333df.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>Enjoy the colorful graphics and ambient music:</strong> Panda’s Village features a charming cartoon style with vibrant colors and cute animations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/010ae6dcf8c1d144b2a36fac91f8792d.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/98296de4bbb317b789b525e0434a1a15.webp?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=40 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Panda’s Village is a real-time strategy and survival game where you take on the role of a brave panda who must protect his village from the invasion of evil monkeys. You will need to build and upgrade houses, defenses, and stores, fight fierce monkeys, purchase and upgrade weapons and magic, and customize your panda with different outfits and accessories. Your goal is to save the village’s Capitol, the heart of your civilization, at all costs. If you die, you start over.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/98296de4bbb317b789b525e0434a1a15.webp?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/75203e027d6683362b698ebec7c80d22.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>Build and manage your village:</strong> Construct houses, shops, defenses, and more to provide resources and security for your panda population. Upgrade your buildings to increase their efficiency and durability. Balance your economy and military to ensure the survival of your village.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/6402fc06da69431b14294a271913b53b.poster.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/6402fc06da69431b14294a271913b53b.webm?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/6402fc06da69431b14294a271913b53b.mp4?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/ef0b998567de4ffe86f477c606f61af2.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>Fight and defend against the monkeys:</strong> The monkeys are relentless and will attack your village from all directions. Use your weapons and magic to fend them off, or recruit other pandas to join your army. Be careful, though, as the monkeys will also use their own tricks and tactics to try to destroy your Capitol.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/792bde2b68a0e5ba2deb04e11a7101eb.poster.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/792bde2b68a0e5ba2deb04e11a7101eb.webm?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/792bde2b68a0e5ba2deb04e11a7101eb.mp4?t=1702089810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/16e890e75b91d8c4d45f64049afd1f36.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>Purchase and upgrade your equipment:</strong> As you progress through the game, you will unlock new weapons and magic that will help you in your battles. You can buy them from the shop. You can also upgrade your panda's characteristics to be stronger, faster, and healthier.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/649bf924b275af4c1a6527e2e1e1819e.poster.avif?t=1702089810\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257630/extras/649bf924b275af4c1a6527e2e1e1819e.webm?t=1702089810\" type=\"vi